{#
/**
 * @file
 * The default template file for e-mails.
 *
 * Available variables:
 * - subject: The subject.
 * - body: The message content.
 * - message: The $message array created and used in the mail building
 *   procedure. Its content varies between cases, but typically contains at
 *   least the following elements:
 *   - id: The message identifier.
 *   - module: The module that handles the building of the message.
 *   - key: The key of the message.
 *   - to: The recipient email address.
 *   - from: The email address of the sender.
 *   - langcode: The langcode to use to compose the e-mail.
 *   - params: The message parameters.
 *
 * This template may be overriden by module and/or mail key, using any of the
 * following template names:
 * - swiftmailer.html.twig: global, used by default.
 * - swiftmailer--mymodule.html.twig: only emails sent by the module "mymodule".
 * - swiftmailer--mymodule--test.html.twig: only emails by the module
 *   "mymodule" with key "test".
 *
 * @see template_preprocess()
 * @see template_preprocess_swiftmailer()
 *
 * @ingroup themeable
 */
#}
{% set v = message.params.v %}
{% set langcode = message.lang %}
<html>
<body>

<table class="email">

  <tr class="header">
    <td>
      <img class="logo" width="193" height="44" alt="{{ message.logoAlt }}" src="{{ message.logo }}">
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr class="body">
    <td>
      <table class="body-table">
        <tr class="body-body">
          <td>
            <div class="wysiwyg">

              {% if langcode == "fr" %}
                <p>Cher / Chère {{ message.name }},</p>
                {{ message.params.body|raw }}
                <p>
                  Merci d’avoir pris le temps de parler avec nous au sujet des initiatives du <a href="https://www.mentoringcanada.ca/fr/">Partenariat canadien de mentorat</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Nous allons également vous envoyer une invitation pour vous inscrire au <strong>Connecteur Mentor</strong> dès que la période d’inscription sera ouverte. Le Connecteur Mentor est une plateforme de recrutement en ligne qui dirigera les futurs mentors et les mentorés vers le programme qui leur convient le mieux. Il s’agit de la première initiative du Portail Mentor Canada qui sera lancé cet été. Le Portail Mentor Canada est un portail national pour les mentors, mentorés et les organismes de mentorat. Le portail offrira des outils technologiques et des ressources créées en collaboration avec des organismes canadiens de mentorat.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <a href="https://www.mentoringcanada.ca/fr/infolettre">Inscrivez-vous à notre liste d’envoi</a> pour recevoir les dernières nouvelles à propos des initiatives du Partenariat canadien de mentorat.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Nous vous remercions de votre soutien et de votre contribution au développement d’un mouvement de mentorat au Canada.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <br>
                  <strong>Véronique Church-Duplessis</strong><br>
                  <a href="mailto:veronique.church-duplessis@mentoringcanada.ca">veronique.church-duplessis@mentoringcanada.ca</a><br>
                  1-800-263-9133 ext. 62<br>
                  Directrice de la recherche et de l’évaluation<br>
                  Partenariat canadien de mentorat
                </p>
              {% else %}
                <p>Dear {{ message.name }},</p>
                <p>
                  Thank you for taking the time to speak with us regarding the work of the <a href="https://www.mentoringcanada.ca/en/">Canadian Mentoring Partnership</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  We will send you an invitation to pre-register for the <strong>Mentor Connector</strong> as soon as it is live. The Mentor Connector is an online recruitment platform that matches volunteer mentors and mentees with the right mentoring program.  This is the first initiative within the Canadian Mentor Portal that we’ll be launching this summer. It is a national gateway for mentors, mentees and the organizations that support them.  The portal will offer technology and resources developed in consultation with Canadian mentoring service providers.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <a href="https://www.mentoringcanada.ca/en/newsletter">Sign up here</a> to receive updates on CMP’s work.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Thank you again for your ongoing support as we work together to build a national mentoring movement in Canada.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <br>
                  <strong>Véronique Church-Duplessis</strong><br>
                  <a href="mailto:veronique.church-duplessis@mentoringcanada.ca">veronique.church-duplessis@mentoringcanada.ca</a><br>
                  1-800-263-9133 ext. 62<br>
                  Director of Research and Evaluation<br>
                  Canadian Mentoring Partnership
                </p>
              {% endif %}

            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr class="footer">
    <td>
      <div class="footer-summary">

        <div class="footer-contact-block">
          <div class="footer-contact-title">{{ "Follow us"|t([],{'langcode': langcode}) }}</div>
          <div class="footer-social">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/mentoringcanada/">
              <img src="{{ message.fb }}" alt="Facebook">
            </a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/MentoringCanada">
              <img src="{{ message.tw }}" alt="Twitter">
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/canadian-mentoring-partnership-partenariat-canadien-de-mentorat/?viewAsMember=true">
              <img src="{{ message.li }}" alt="LinkedIn">
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mentorcanada/">
              <img src="{{ message.ig }}" alt="Instagram">
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYExa1ehADYg-kzG7lSmPoQ/">
              <img src="{{ message.yt }}" alt="YouTube">
            </a>
          </div>
          <p>#MentoringCanada</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-contact-block">
          <div class="footer-contact-title">{{ "Contact us"|t([],{'langcode': langcode}) }}</div>
          <a href="{{ message.globalSettings.phoneLink }}">{{ message.globalSettings.phoneDisplayWithExtension }}</a>
          <br>
          <a href="{{ message.globalSettings.emailLink }}">{{ message.globalSettings.emailDisplay }}</a>
          <br>
          <a href="mentoringcanada.ca/{{ langcode }}" target="_blank">mentoringcanada.ca</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-contact-block">
          <div class="footer-contact-title">{{ "Mailing address"|t([],{'langcode': langcode}) }}</div>
          <p>
            {{ message.globalSettings .addressName }}
            <br>
            {{ message.globalSettings .addressLine1 }}
            <br>
            {{ message.globalSettings .addressLine2 }}
            <br>
            {{ message.globalSettings .addressLine3 }}
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-contact-block">
          <p>{{ "Join our"|t([],{'langcode': langcode}) }} <a href="https://mentoringcanada.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe?u=a67929939be415eba75c93a0b&id=7d099210dd" target="_blank">{{ "mailing list"|t([],{'langcode': langcode}) }}</a></p>
          <p>&copy;{{ 'now'|date('Y') }} {{ message.globalSettings.addressName }}</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </td>
  </tr>

</table>

</body>
</html>
